Package io.servicetalk.transport.netty.internal

Class ExecutionContextExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.servicetalk.transport.netty.internal.ExecutionContextExtension
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecutionContext<ExecutionStrategy>, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.AfterAllCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.AfterEachCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.BeforeAllCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.BeforeEachCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.Extension
    public final class ExecutionContextExtension
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.AfterEachCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.BeforeEachCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.AfterAllCallback, org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.BeforeAllCallback, ExecutionContext<ExecutionStrategy>
    An Extension that creates and disposes an ExecutionContext for your test case or suite.

    Can be used with a RegisterExtension field. If used with a class static field then use setClassLevel(true) to create contained ExecutionContext instance only once for all tests in class.
